Shopping district



Unfortunately, the shops all shut down from 1:30 in the afternoon until around 5:00. The correct plan would have been to shop first, then go to the beach.
Taken Friday, September 14, 2001, 03:37:04pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 408kb
